                 Doctor Who - The Quiz Game
                                           v2.0

                       Introduction
                                   
                                           
This is a simple multiple choice quiz game based on Doctor Who.
It features questions about all the Doctors from the first Doctor
to the Seventh Doctor, and the adventures they were invloved with.

There are also some questions about behind the scenes and other
issues related to Doctor Who. Little bits of extra information
sometimes accompany questions.

NOTE: Due to the fact that the program is written in AMOS, the Quiz
Game is not friendly with screen blankers. If you have a screen blanker
in operation, turn it off. If you still have it in operation during
the game, you will probably find that mouse pointer disappears. If this
happens, press LAmiga-A to return to Workbench, where you can deactivate
the blanker.

