                        Requirements
                        
                     
There are very few requirements for this game. The requirements:

o An Amiga (any Amiga should do, although I haven't tried it on
  1.3 machines. It definately works on 2.x machines, although I
  haven't tried it on 3.x machines)
  
o Any form of disk media (hard or floppy)

o A knowledge of Doctor Who (This could be very useful indeed)

o NO screen blanker. It does not work with this game 
  (See @{" Introduction " link Introduction})

I'm not sure about memory requirements. It should work with 1Mb or
over, but it may work with 512k.

